These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
House: cape-cod, cottage, ranch-style, townhouse
4 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, billiard, snooker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, trance, house, electronic
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, amaryllis, daisy, marigold
 1. the fan of trance is not to the right of the fan of country##8
 2. the person who growsbegonia is not to the left of the person who growsbegonia##8
 3. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the fan of country is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
 5. the person who growsbegonia is not to the right of the person who growsbegonia##8
 6. the person playing billiard is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 7. the cottage house is somewhere to the right of the cape-cod house##5
 8. the person playing snooker is between the person who growsamaryllis and the fan of trance##2
 9. the person who growsmarigold is the person playing billiard##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the townhouse house##1
11. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
12. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the cottage house##5
13. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the person who growsmarigold##8
14. the cottage house is the person who growsdaisy##1
15. the cottage house is not the fan of trance##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| House         | cape-cod     | cottage   | townhouse | ranch-style |
| Game   | scrabble | snooker   | canasta   | billiard  |
| Music-Genre         | trance  | house  | electronic  | country |
| Flower     | begonia    | daisy | amaryllis     | marigold    |

