.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, fisherman, writer, bartender
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, russian, mexican
House: ranch-style, futuristic, townhouse, victorian
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, poker, canasta
 1. the townhouse house is between the person playing mah-jongg and the futuristic house##2
 2. the fisherman is not to the right of the person playing snooker##8
 3. the fisherman is on the left or right of the chinese##3
 4. the software-developer is not to the right of the person playing canasta##8
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the futuristic house##8
 6. the mexican is not to the right of the bartender##8
 7. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
 8. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
 9. the ranch-style house is the person playing snooker##1
10. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
11. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the townhouse house##8
12. the bartender is on the left of the fisherman##1
13. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
14. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
15. the software-developer is on the far left or far right##3
16. the russian is on the right of the chinese##1
17. the software-developer is not to the right of the futuristic house##8
18. the dutch is not to the right of the person playing snooker##8
19. the bartender is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
