.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, february, november, january
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goldfish, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, bus, van, airplane
City: berlin, london, boston, colone
 1. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
 5. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8
 7. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the bird is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
12. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | march    | january   | november | february |
| Pet   | bird     | goldfish  | snake   | chinchilla      |
| Transport   | bus | trike    | van      | airplane       |
| City         | boston    | berlin | colone   | london    |

