 6. the person who likes white is not to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##8
 7. the person who likes lilac is not to the left of the person playing go##8
 8. the person driving the trike is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the person playing canasta##8
10. the person traveling to berlin is not to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##8
11. the person who likes amber is between the person playing canasta and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
12. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who likes white##1
13. the person driving the trike is not to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
14. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3

.:: Answer ::.
