16. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the fonseca-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Sport           | skiing | weightlifting       | soccer      | surfing  |
| Cigar   | montecristo    | oliveros | fonseca   | ritmeester   |
| Food   | tomato   | corn          | radish      | lemon  |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | mirinda      | water | lemonade |

